				</div>
				<div class="newsD-article-title">
					<h2>汉中市铁路中心医院关于2024年招聘疼痛科医生岗位考试的公告</h2>
					<p style="font-size:14px;">汉中市第一医院（汉中市妇女儿童医院）官网&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="font-size:14px;">2024-07-10 14:45:24</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;来源：&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;阅读量：11374</p>
				</div>
				<div class="newsD-article-content">
					<p>
						<p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><br/></p><p style="text-indent:0;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:center;line-height:37px"><span style="font-family: 方正小标宋简体;font-size: 29px">汉中市铁路中心医院</span><span style="font-family: 方正小标宋简体;font-size: 29px">关于</span><span style="font-family: 方正小标宋简体;font-size: 29px">202</span><span style="font-family: 方正小标宋简体;font-size: 29px">4</span><span style="font-family: 方正小标宋简体;font-size: 29px">年</span><span style="font-family: 方正小标宋简体;font-size: 29px">招聘</span><span style="font-family: 方正小标宋简体;font-size: 29px">疼痛科医生岗位考试</span><span style="font-family: 方正小标宋简体;font-size: 29px">的</span><span style="font-family: 方正小标宋简体;font-size: 29px">公告</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">根据</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">202</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">4</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">年</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">6</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">月</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">25</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">日汉中市</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">铁路中心医院</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">发布《</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">汉中市铁路中心医院招聘疼痛科医生的公告</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">》的有关规定，我院</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">于</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">7月5日完成了报名及资格审查工作，</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">其中符合报名资格条件的应聘人员共</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">5</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">人</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">（详见附件</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">）</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">。现将</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">考试相关事项公告</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">如下：</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:黑体;font-size:21px">一、技能测试</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">（一）技能测试时间及地点</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">1.时间：2024</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">年</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">7</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">月</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">13</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">日（</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">星期六</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">）</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">8</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">:</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">20，请参加人员于当日8:10到汉中市铁路中心医院4号楼（行政楼二层）人事科签到。</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">2.技能测试地点：</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">汉中市铁路中心医院门诊四楼疼痛科。</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">（</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">二</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">）</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">技能测试</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">所持资料</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">二代身份证原件（含有效期内的临时身份证）。</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">（三）测试方式</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">采取接诊实操方式，每人时间为</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">10分钟。</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><span style="font-family: 黑体;font-size: 21px">二</span><span style="font-family: 黑体;font-size: 21px">、面试</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">（一）面试原则</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">坚持公开、平等、竞争、择优的原则，按照德才兼备的标准和岗位所需的资格条件组织实施。</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">（</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">二</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">）面试时间及地点：</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">1.面试时间：</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">2024</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">年</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">7</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">月</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">13</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">日（</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">星期六</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">）</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">9</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">:</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">3</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">0</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">。</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">2</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">.面试地点：汉中市铁路中心医院行政楼</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">2号</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">会议室</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">。</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">（人事科隔壁）</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">（</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">三</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">）面试所持资料</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">二代身份证原件（含有效期内的临时身份证）。</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">（</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">四</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">）面试方式和内容</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">1.面试方式：采取结构化面试的方式进行，面试时间为</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">6</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">分钟。</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">2.面试内容：主要测评应聘人员的综合分析能力、逻辑思维能力、语言组织及表达能力、应变能力和仪容、仪表等。</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><span style="font-family: 黑体;font-size: 21px">三、考试总成绩计算方法</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">（一）</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">考试总成绩</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">=</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">技能测试成绩</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">×50%+</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">面试成绩</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">×50%+加分成绩。</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><strong><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;font-size: 21px">加分成绩：</span></strong><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">1.具有大学本科学历者+5分；2.具有本科学士学位证者+5分；3.具有执业医师证者+5分；4.具有住院医师规培合格证者+10分；5.具有硕士学位证者+10分；6.具有医师系列中级职称者+5分；7.具有医师系列高级职称者+10分。（以上加分项同时具备时可累计计算）</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">（二）面试成绩按百分制计算，保留小数点后</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">2位，第三位小数不进行四舍五入，计算方法如下：共有</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">7名评委打分，去掉一个最高分、去掉一个最低分，其余5名评委打分相加后的平均分为应聘人员的面试成绩</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">。</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><span style="font-family: 黑体;font-size: 21px">四、公布成绩和确定体检人员名单</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">（一）面试结束后，按照招聘岗位计划数</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">1:1的比例，根据应聘人员考试</span></span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">总</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">成绩由高到低确定参加体检人选</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">，如考试总成绩相同时，以技能测试成绩高者优先。</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">（二）应聘人员的</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">总</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">成绩和进入体检人员名单将在汉中市</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">铁路中心医院官网</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">公告，同时公告体检工作安排，请应聘人员及时查看公告并保持电话通畅。</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><span style="font-family: 黑体;font-size: 21px">五、其他事项</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">（一）</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">为了确保参考顺利进行，应聘人员应提前查询交通路线，合理安排出行时间，注意交通安全。请</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">考生</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">按要求时间提前到场。</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">（二）</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">应聘人员必须严格遵守考试纪律，维护良好的秩序。</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">（三）</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">对提供虚假证明、不如实告知实际情况的</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">及违规作弊人员</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">，取消本次招录资格，并按有关法律规定追究相关责任。</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">人事科</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">联系电话：</span><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">0916-2212561</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">监察室监督电话：</span><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">0916-2692140</span></p><p style="text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋;font-size:21px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-indent:43px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;font-size: 21px"><span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">附件</span> </span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;font-size: 21px">&nbsp;<span style="font-family:仿宋_GB2312">疼痛科医生岗位资格审查合格名单</span></span><span style="font-family: 仿宋_GB2312;font-size: 21px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph;line-height:37px"><span style=";font-family:仿宋_GB2312;font-size:21px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="text-align: right; line-height: 37px;"><span style="text-indent: 253px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21px;">汉中市铁路中心医院</span></p><p style="text-align: right; line-height: 37px;"><span style="text-indent: 265px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21px;">202</span><span style="text-indent: 265px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21px;">4</span><span style="text-indent: 265px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21px;">年</span><span style="text-indent: 265px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21px;">7</span><span style="text-indent: 265px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21px;">月</span><span style="text-indent: 265px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21px;">9</span><span style="text-indent: 265px; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 21px;">日&nbsp; &nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>						附件：<a class="download" href='/home/plugs/download/id/1547.html'>附件 疼痛科医生岗位资格审查合格名单.xls</a>
																	</p>
					<!--<a href="#">返回</a>-->
				</div>
				<div class="expert_details_bottom">
										<span>上一篇：</span><a href="/article/notice/1157.html" class="toe">汉中市铁路中心医院 6月招聘医学检验工作人员拟聘人选公示</a>
										<span>下一篇：</span><a href="/article/notice/1159.html" class="toe">后勤零星维修公司遴选(第二次)采购项目磋商结果公告</a>
									</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>
